name: Move Multipurpose Template 2.2 Preview
description:
Overview


Move Multipurpose Template comes with a multitude of carefully designed page layouts; purpose-built content blocks, that when pieced together, create stunning professional layouts.


To make your workflow as productive as possible, we created 5 high-quality pre-built home pages and 28 additional pages that you can use as the basis for a website you create.


Features


- Best for App, SaaS Product, Software, and Digital Products.

- A clean, modern, multi-purpose design that can be adapted and used for any website design.

- 5 Amazing designed landing pages. No more looking for inspiration or starting from scratch.

- 28 Additional pages to display your content, whether it's a blog or portfolio.

- 80+ Ready Edit Blocks. You can develop a ready-made website layout in a short time.

- 40+ UI Components. Create new content using pre-built interface elements.

- Strong focus on typography, usability, and overall user-experience.

- Move components, change their color, and resize without losing quality.

- We aim to support you in a timely and effective manner.

- By purchasing this product now, you will receive updates for free!


If you liked our product then we will be grateful if you recommend it to others.
